pageContext.claim: “Now, if this weren't the greatest thing -- I really believe. Now, it's been said, but Make America Great Again. Ronald Reagan used seldom 'Let's Make America Great.' Close, but not the same. Let's -- apostrophe S. You don't want the apostrophe.”
pageContext.analysis: Actually, Reagan's slogan was: "Let's make America great again."  In other words, it was virtually identical to Trump's slogan.
